Upgrading LConf

Upgrading from 1.2.x to 1.3.x
-----------------------------

- LConf*.pl scripts are moved into $prefix/bin by default
- contrib/lconf_deploy.sh is renamed to contrib/LConfDeploy.sh
- inheritance of attributes across main and template trees. 
This feature is disabled by default. To enable it you simply need to set a config option in config.pm. Please let the feature disabled if you're not sure about it or read section "TreeRewrite" of the documentation for further information.

